title: Any Flv Player Portable
description:
This is a portable version Any Flv Player

I don't take credit for this app  I just made it portable so you can take it with you 

I have scanned it for viruses and it scans clean    but it's a good idea to check it yourself . This was made portable on XP pro machine  and I have tested it on windows XP & XP pro   I have not tested it on vista

There is no need to install just copy the file to your desktop or usb key  and just click on the Any Flv Player.exe file
